WEBVTT

00:00:01.500 --> 00:00:06.333
American manufacturing is moving again.

00:00:06.333 --> 00:00:11.667
In REINDUSTRIALIZE, you do not watch from the sidelines. You build the company.

00:00:11.667 --> 00:00:17.333
Start in an empty garage. Choose your founder. Learn from Zach.

00:00:17.333 --> 00:00:23.000
Win the work, order certified material, and cut stock.

00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:28.333
Set tools, read real G and M code, and inspect the first article.

00:00:28.333 --> 00:00:34.667
Then hire the team, expand the floor, and turn one reliable job into a manufacturing powerhouse.

00:00:34.667 --> 00:00:40.500
This is where builders learn how production really works—

00:00:40.500 --> 00:00:45.333
one decision, one part, and one promise kept at a time.

00:00:45.333 --> 00:00:48.000
Your first shift starts now.
